{
  "stem": "23498.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had their own house, but the times were very hard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she arrived there, and the woman said, if Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Strosberg sent her treasure, we have to keep it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This-- those words.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So my mother was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So then I went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I went-- it was-- from the big ghetto, it was a-- a big wall.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was in-- late in the evening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You have to go through the-- on the, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, what you climb.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ladder.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, such--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Terrible.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the ladder, on the top was where pieces of glass jump.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, it was no man's land.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If a German saw someone, kill on the spot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He killed whoever it was, whether it was a person, or an animal, he killed on the spot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I had to run.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had directions, and had to run to the other ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then, over there, I-- I slept a few hours, and it was still-- it will still late, but it was some [INAUDIBLE], they call it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A few people who work on the [INAUDIBLE] side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they-- this why I went with them, but it was-- it was very interesting how it-- it was about 50 people, and four in a row.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first-- it-- it was a German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably someone was paid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That what I reckon, a Polish-- a policeman or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "German wouldn't be, but a Polish policeman, probably.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it-- a German-- one or two were there, and the Polish policeman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when we walk, we walked like this-- from the first row, when the German looked another direction, one of the men disappeared.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was an empty space, yes?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then you--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
